          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Geoffrey Robinson MP Retweeted Jeremy Corbyn</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I'm looking forward to meeting Coventry's <a href="/Coventry_Police" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="21696855"><s>@</s><b>Coventry_Police</b></a> Commander <a href="/CovCommanderWMP" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="2576482208"><s>@</s><b>CovCommanderWMP</b></a> this Friday to discuss the rise in crime and Police funding cuts <a href="/hashtag/stoptorypolicecuts?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>stoptorypolicecuts</b></a><a href="https://t.co/SohlXj0llO" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/967859209265086465" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/967859209265086465"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/967859209265086465</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Changing the law on organ donation could save as many as 500 lives a year. This Friday I'll be backing Geoffrey Robinsons Private Members Bill, which seeks to introduce a national opt-out system for donation in England. See more here: <a href="https://t.co/eUK8eOrTDJ" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://bit.ly/2EIyWhX" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://bit.ly/2EIyWhX"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">bit.ly/2EIyWhX</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a><a href="https://t.co/W8CUOxQn2Q" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/W8CUOxQn2Q</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0"><a href="/hashtag/OTD?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>OTD</b></a> 1973. The first graduates receive their degrees from the <a href="/OpenUniversity" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="14049061"><s>@</s><b>OpenUniversity</b></a>. Harold Wilson had launched the programme in 1969 to entice low income students to university. He later remarked that it was the greatest achievement of his premiership.<a href="https://t.co/63wW9uHbZj" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/63wW9uHbZj</a></p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">As my Private Members' Bill on Organ Donation gathers pace, I'll be meeting next week with Sally Johnson, Director of Organ Donation &amp; Transplantation for the NHS to discuss the draft legislation.   <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">To me, culture in Cov means bringing people together. Should we win City of culture 2021 we could change the lives of thousands of people in the City and the wider region. Cov is undergoing a renaissance, this could be the catalyst for big things!

 <a href="/Coventry2021" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="3328906445"><s>@</s><b>Coventry2021</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/ThisisCoventry?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>ThisisCoventry</b></a><a href="https://t.co/mADYcyPViB" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/mADYcyPViB</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Community spirit is another cracking reason why <a href="/Coventry2021" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="3328906445"><s>@</s><b>Coventry2021</b></a> is perfect for the <a href="/hashtag/UKCityofCulture2021?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>UKCityofCulture2021</b></a>.

        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>

  </ul>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Geoffrey Robinson MP Retweeted The Labour Party</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Giving football fans a true stake in their clubs and sharing power &amp; responsibility would benefit clubs like <a href="/Coventry_City" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="70677962"><s>@</s><b>Coventry_City</b></a> extremely.<a href="https://t.co/qm4pOcx4yi" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/UKLabour/status/868412199303348224" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/UKLabour/status/868412199303348224"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/UKLabour/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/868412199303348224</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Geoffrey Robinson MP added,</p>
